  "prompt": "What percentage of Quora users ask and answer questions?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, the specific percentage of Quora users who both ask and answer questions is not publicly available through Quora's official statistics. Quora does not typically release detailed breakdowns of user behavior in such granular terms. However, it is generally understood that a notable portion of users engage in both activities, though the majority of users may primarily consume content rather than actively contribute by asking or answering questions.\n\nFor more precise and up-to-date statistics, you might consider checking Quora's official reports or contacting them directly, as well as looking at studies or surveys conducted by third parties on user engagement on the platform.",
